						<article class="clearfix full-article has-hero-image  time_article " id="article-3600230" data-article="3600230" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
  <header class="article-header">
    
    <section class="tags ">
  		  <a class="brand-tag brand-time-tag" href="http://time.com/" data-bypass="true">TIME</a>


            <a class="section-tag" itemprop="articleSection" href="http://time.com/tech/" data-event="section-tech">Tech</a>

            <a class="topic-tag" itemprop="articleSection" href="http://time.com/tag/smartphones/" data-event="tag-smartphones" data-bypass="true">Smartphones</a>

      </section>
    <h2 class="article-title" itemprop="headline">President Obama Forgot His BlackBerry Today</h2>
  <div class="article-sub-headline">
    <div class="article-meta">

        <ul class="article-authors">
            <li class="article-author ">
              <span class="byline"><a itemprop="author" href="http://time.com/author/alex-fitzpatrick/">Alex Fitzpatrick</a></span>
              <a class="author-twitter" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/alexjamesfitz">@alexjamesfitz</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <time class="publish-date" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2014-11-21 14:38:42" pubdate>Nov. 21, 2014</time>
      
    </div>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a class="expand-share" href="javascript:void 0;" data-event="exp-micro" title="Click to view article share options">SHARE</a>
    <span class="social-links-tooltip">
    	<a class="time-icons time-icons-mail social-link-mail" href="mailto:?subject=President%20Obama%20Forgot%20His%20BlackBerry%20Today%20%7C%20TIME&body=President%20Obama%20Forgot%20His%20BlackBerry%20Today%0A%0AWe%27ve%20all%20been%20there%2C%20Barack%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3600230%2Fobama-blackberry%2F" data-event="email" title="Click to Email this article"></a>
    	<a class="time-icons time-icons-fb social-link-fb popup" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3600230%2Fobama-blackberry%2F" data-event="fb-share" title="Click to post this article to Facebook"></a>
    	<a class="time-icons time-icons-tw social-link-tw popup" href="#" data-href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5HMd-f6Ae&text=President%20Obama%20forgot%20his%20BlackBerry%20today&via=Techland" data-event="tweet" title="Click to Tweet this article"></a>
    	<a class="time-icons time-icons-gplus social-link-gplus popup" href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3600230%2Fobama-blackberry%2F" data-event="google+" title="Click to post this article to Google+"></a>
    	<a class="time-icons time-icons-linkedin social-link-linkedin popup" href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3600230%2Fobama-blackberry%2F&title=President+Obama+Forgot+His+BlackBerry+Today" data-event="linkedin" title="Click to post this article to LinkedIn"></a>
    	
    </span>    </div>
  </div>  </header>  <section class="article-body" itemprop="articleBody">
    
    <figure class="wide">
      <img src="http://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2014/11/obama-blackberry.jpg?w=280" itemprop="image" alt="U.S. President Barack Obama holds up his BlackBerry device after he returned inside the White House to retrieve it, after boarding Marine One on the South Lawn of the White House in Washington on Nov. 21, 2014." srcset="http://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2014/11/obama-blackberry.jpg?w=1680 800w, http://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2014/11/obama-blackberry.jpg?w=1680 800w 2x"/>
      <figcaption class="image-caption">
        <span class="caption">U.S. President Barack Obama holds up his BlackBerry device after he returned inside the White House to retrieve it, after boarding Marine One on the South Lawn of the White House in Washington on Nov. 21, 2014. </span>
        <span class="credit">Larry Downingâ€”Reuters</span>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
	<h2 class="article-excerpt" itemprop="alternativeHeadline">We've all been there, Barack</h2>
    <p>At one point or another, we&#8217;ve all left our phones at home, only to realize it after we&#8217;re already in the car, bus, or subway. Well, count one more victim of smartphone amnesia: President Obama.</p>
<p>Obama reportedly left the White House to board Marine One earlier Friday &mdash; only to realize once on board that he left his BlackBerry back in his office. He hurried off the presidential chopper, grabbed his phone and headed back outside, waving the device in the air and telling reporters &#8220;Didn&#8217;t you guys ever forget something?,&#8221; Bloomberg <a href="http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-11-21/blackberry-scores-free-ad-as-obama-retrieves-smartphone.html?hootPostID=03e97b5baa8ec81ac1d21d8aed5a4cdb" target="_blank">reports</a>.</p>
<p>Obama is a longtime BlackBerry user, and government offices in general remain one of the company&#8217;s strongest markets.</p>
<aside class="right-rail-module rr-share" data-name="rr-share"><span class="social-links">
    <a class="time-icons time-icons-mail social-link-mail" href="mailto:?subject=President%20Obama%20Forgot%20His%20BlackBerry%20Today%20%7C%20TIME&body=President%20Obama%20Forgot%20His%20BlackBerry%20Today%0A%0AWe%27ve%20all%20been%20there%2C%20Barack%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3600230%2Fobama-blackberry%2F" data-event="email" title="Click to Email this article"></a>
    <a class="time-icons time-icons-fb social-link-fb popup" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3600230%2Fobama-blackberry%2F" data-event="fb-share" title="Click to post this article to Facebook"></a>
    <a class="time-icons time-icons-tw social-link-tw popup" href="#" data-href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5HMd-f6Ae&text=President%20Obama%20forgot%20his%20BlackBerry%20today&via=Techland" data-event="tweet" title="Click to Tweet this article"></a>
    <a class="time-icons time-icons-linkedin social-link-linkedin popup" href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3600230%2Fobama-blackberry%2F&title=President+Obama+Forgot+His+BlackBerry+Today" data-event="linkedin" title="Click to post this article to LinkedIn"></a>
